{"tid":2318052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"最新消息！詭辯血清抗體陽轉率 打臉印尼數據擺烏龍 支企否認支那疫苗3%失敗率！","createTime":"2020-12-09T04:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T12:40:35.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"63a7fdceb978b4f35f1ff1490a29d5d7ab518600","tid":2318052,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T04:57:58.000Z","msg":"外電報導，印尼國營藥廠聲稱，中國科興生技製造的武漢<br />\n肺炎疫苗防護效力高達97%。但科興8日坦承，97%的數字應是「血清抗體陽轉率」，至於這<br />\n款疫苗的有效率目前尚未確定。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，總部位在北京的科興生技（Sinovac Biotech）8日以發言人名義表示，<br />\n這款疫苗在印尼進行的最後階段試驗中，接種者有97%「產生了抗體」，但「有效率」目前<br />\n尚未確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3gqIC4e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3gqIC4e&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=ccf4e80f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3gqIC4e</a>"},{"pid":"6a4b3ee2bdd5fa81e2590edd9c661a1eb606e82d","tid":2318052,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"突發！高達3%無效！印尼期中試驗數據顯示支那制疫苗效力成疑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2317629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2317629</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6d222fc20e28e345a16b693efa7dc6fd74bdd449","tid":2318052,"uid":66898,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:05:49.000Z","msg":"隻隻字都識但寫埋一齊又唔識<br />\n究竟講緊咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39581299137cf21912380ef147641f024f4dccd","tid":2318052,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:19:46.000Z","msg":"無效打多針會唔會有效？"},{"pid":"7617bd9efc2877152e9a94f3fa2f268f96bf54a0","tid":2318052,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d222fc20e28e345a16b693efa7dc6fd74bdd449","tid":2318052,"uid":66898,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:05:49.000Z","msg":"隻隻字都識但寫埋一齊又唔識<br />\n究竟講緊咩野<img src=\"